    "body": "The whole JSON structure is documented in [Compiler Input and Output JSON Description](https://docs.soliditylang.org/en/latest/using-the-compiler.html#compiler-input-and-output-json-description).\r\n\r\nThe `--optimize-runs` option is called `runs` there:\r\n```json\r\n\r\n\"optimizer\": {\r\n    \"enabled\": true,\r\n    \"runs\": 200\r\n}\r\n```",
